"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/N1O01S6xHxmFOqPWv7-ay.png?height=1602&width=2647)\\n\\nThe matrix is everywhere\\n\\nsome matrix is others' built for you\\nsome metrix is that you built for yourself\\n\\nwe all live in matrix\\n\\n展开来说，就是你生活这个世界上，你所遵循的律法政策，风俗习惯，社会舆论，公司制度，职场规则，家庭伦理，等等，都是别人给你建的matrix\\n\\n而你的处世方式，你的思想框架，你的认知体系，你的评价标准，你的爱憎好恶，都是你自己给自己建的matrix\\n\\n我们随时随地都生活在matrix之中，与此同时，也一刻不停地在给别人、也给自己建造matrix\",\"timestamp\":1642415512,\"title\":\"The matrix is everywhere\"},\"digest\":\"QXKd-2bK_3ugf19nLN2QCEnuQxiw9x-4ZFYNobrLcRQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x3E1Cdb8536f9A1e1ff18a5Eaa653A0884818D3AA\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6bHDNgrDbASzcACxIPC1-IhwhkGbDjNBxzuzi5Fiunk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"6q0jmbZNJjz4Cd_XRH1-ApZdBTRph_USjTzMORn51hM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8dNGOIIfRyRMYUzk-9E9Z9KK3qI7t0WI-3EuiIwFGwDuUOQ7Jel5Q--QMPr3adtyIix_uSHXK4lBWHn0z7z-iA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x23a3cf863f6195c42622a74277e9299dfcbb6c9fdfc0df53a8bbf27912b1b13521124e5a64f85743d92ca58850a2394d605153c5c11aa597ab83eb81ab4d5cde1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6bHDNgrDbASzcACxIPC1-IhwhkGbDjNBxzuzi5Fiunk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"6q0jmbZNJjz4Cd_XRH1-ApZdBTRph_USjTzMORn51hM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"QXKd-2bK_3ugf19nLN2QCEnuQxiw9x-4ZFYNobrLcRQ\"}"